<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>حَافظ وَلَو<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>هُوَ<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>نَائِم وَمَعَ فَتحه ونومه غير حرز لَيْلًا وَكَذَا نَهَارا فِي الْأَصَح<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>وَمُقَابِله تكون حرْزا اعْتِمَادًا على نظر الْجِيرَان<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
